Fix glibc-2.17 intl/plural.y for Bison 3.x compatibility

Bison 3.x deprecated YYPARSE_PARAM and YYLEX_PARAM macros.
This patch updates plural.y to use the modern %define and %param directives.

Changes:
- Replace deprecated %pure_parser with %define api.pure full
- Add %parse-param and %lex-param directives
- Update yylex/yyerror signatures for bison 3.x

This patch applies AFTER centos7-all.patch.

